Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:49.16,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Day by day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:52.89,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うんざりだよね  だから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:57.68,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂々と断っちゃう　キミになりなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:01:58.89,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my boy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:02.53,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キッパリしなきゃ　嘘に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:07.60,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,付きあってられないよ　狭い世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:10.16,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自分で見つけた　myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:12.50,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好きになって当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:14.96,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,くだらないやり方蹴って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:19.93,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すべてはあたしが決める!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:22.35,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(I say,I say my heaven)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:24.85,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Super Driver　突進まかせて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:26.77,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんてったって前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:28.58,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不可能！」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.72,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Don't you stop me)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:31.89,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛び越えて　Take it eazy,Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:34.41,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大勝利って同感もちろん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.31,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうなったって快感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:38.03,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「反省会？」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:39.40,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Get back to wild)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:41.44,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それより　さあ　急いでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:46.07,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あれもこれも未体験　いつだってムリヤリ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:50.98,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まるでまるで未経験　これからしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:55.71,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あれもこれも未体験　いつだってトツゼン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:03:00.52,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まるでまるで未経験　それがどうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:49.16,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Day by day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:52.89,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為無聊之極
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:57.68,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才必須堂堂正正地拒絕　如你一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:01:58.89,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my boy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:02.53,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須對謊話斬釘截鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:07.60,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這不能相處的狹窄世界內
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:10.16,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現自己　myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:12.50,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會喜歡上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:14.96,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把無聊的東西一腳踢開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:19.93,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都由我來決定！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:22.35,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(I say,I say my heaven)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:24.85,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Super Driver　隨我衝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:26.77,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管一切向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:28.58,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不可能！」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.72,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Don't you stop me)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:31.89,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們來飛越　Take it eazy,Go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:34.41,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是取得大勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.31,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法阻擋的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:38.03,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「反省會？」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:39.40,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(Get back to wild)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:41.44,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個　來吧　加速吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:46.07,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個那個也還沒體驗　無論何時都要硬幹下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:50.98,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完完全全地沒有經驗　現在就去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:55.71,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個那個也還沒體驗　無論何時都要馬上行動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:03:00.52,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完完全全地沒有經驗　那又怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:46.05,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}空から落ちてきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.26,0:23:48.86,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全ての願いを乗せて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:53.43,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ひとつの星にはちょっと重かったかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.08,0:23:56.66,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}やっぱり何かヘンだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.78,0:23:59.27,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}心のキミが消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.47,0:24:03.62,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}確かに憶えてるって言えるのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:05.10,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}止マレ！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.26,0:24:08.89,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}過去は自分のもの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.05,0:24:13.35,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}当然　誰とも取り替えたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.61,0:24:14.56,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}なぜなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.77,0:24:19.72,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}バースデイだった　私達には
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.95,0:24:22.69,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}出会いが生まれたときに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.89,0:24:25.07,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}初めての夢が見える
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.23,0:24:30.05,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}どうしようかって　悩んだ事も
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.43,0:24:34.02,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}いま思えば笑えるほどだったよね
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.15,0:24:38.89,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう忘れてた　キミを探そう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:46.05,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}僅僅只因從天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.26,0:23:48.86,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}便要承擔全部願望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:53.43,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}對於一顆小小流星　是否有些沉重？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.08,0:23:56.66,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果然有哪裡出了錯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.78,0:23:59.27,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}心中你已消失不見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.47,0:24:03.62,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}「沒忘掉你」這話　又要怎麼說出？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:05.10,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}停下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.26,0:24:08.89,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}過去只屬於自己
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.05,0:24:13.35,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}當然不會將其交給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.61,0:24:14.56,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}為什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.77,0:24:19.72,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}生日那一天　大家在此處相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.95,0:24:22.69,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}但在那天的初夢前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.89,0:24:25.07,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我們早已相知相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.23,0:24:30.05,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}之前那不知如何是好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.43,0:24:34.02,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}此刻回想　卻是那般可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.15,0:24:38.89,edzw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}已經忘了嗎　那來找你囉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一個慵懶  而又正常到了極點的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盂蘭盆會後的盛夏的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視中正在播放的  是跟我一點關係都沒有的同縣選手的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出於對弱者的同情心  我不由得支持著正處於落後的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這時手機卻大聲嚷嚷了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.39,0:00:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春日啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天很閒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.57,0:00:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩點整全員在車站前集合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.70,0:00:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕描淡寫地掛斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼就知道我今天很閒的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.47,0:00:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我可也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…  雖說我什麼計劃也沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.25,0:01:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.18,0:01:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘跟你說了  帶一套泳裝騎車過來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  帶上足夠的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.22,0:01:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上  Over～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好煩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:15.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打手現正悠閒地跑向三壘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.08,0:01:18.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投手鈴木  在投手丘上一副崩潰的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.34,0:01:21.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是慘不忍睹的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.67,0:01:22.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真淒慘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.48,0:01:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  沒有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.70,0:01:30.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人向投手鈴木發出噓聲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.30,0:01:33.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就是8：0了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:36.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽進入了艱巨的時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:15.44,staffbiaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\fn方正黑体_GBK\pos(235,294)\fs27\an5}Endless Eight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:15.44,staffbiaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\fn方正黑体_GBK\pos(235,370)\an5}漫無止境的八月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了  阿虛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多拿點幹勁出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然讓本團長等你  你以為自己是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要懲罰啦  懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明就提前了15分鐘來  為什麼每次都是最後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  全都到齊了  出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉  你就載實玖瑠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和有希坐阿虛後面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姑且問一句  去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是去市民游泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天當然要有夏天的樣子  要做有夏天特色的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的時間可是一去不返的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在就要行動  在這個只有一次的高一的暑假裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的時間啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這消毒液的氣味  真給人一種實在的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來～啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:29.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（禁止跳水  危險！）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊過來  水溫溫的很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就看不見到處貼的那些禁止跳水的文字說明嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過很讓人欣慰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得  涼宮同學也學會了有常識性的娛樂方法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然打個電話過來  單方面地說好就掛的邀請方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在不能說得上是常識性的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:05:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  笑得那麼開心的涼宮同學  是不會做什麼震動這個世界的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心  自從上次合宿以來  也沒引起過什麼讓人注目的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這會兒  對涼宮同學而言也好  對我們來說也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界就是和平的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是  實玖瑠親手做的三明治哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝稱讚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再吃一塊炸雞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠  給我倒茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實  非常和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是市民泳池  倒是個更適合平民泳池這名字的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  實玖瑠你在幹什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種過暑假的方法倒也不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些就是我的團員們  說什麼都會聽的  所以隨便吩咐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著考慮了下今後的活動計劃  如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣來度過已經所剩無幾的暑假的計劃表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SOS團的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  暑假只剩下兩週了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得還有很多事情沒做呢  要一起都做完哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  在暑假不能不做的事情…嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏期合宿  游泳池  盆舞  煙火匯演  打工  天體觀測…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個表上的東西要在兩週之內都做完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有別的想要做的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  我想撈金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  撈金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼明天開始實行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近有什麼地方明天會跳盆舞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有煙火匯演也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少查過了再給我實行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去查吧  回頭聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  別忘了撈金魚哦  這可是實玖瑠的強烈要求哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:20.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼總是我付錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你遲到了  這是當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天可別讓人等了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  今天就此解散
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  現在開始每天都玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天早晨  將我的懶覺奪走的又是春日打來的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到跳盆舞的會場了  時間是今晚  地點是市民運動場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧她能時機正好地找到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中正半懷佩服時  春日說出了這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去買浴衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠和有希都說沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買一整套的話就會便宜  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日擅自為朝比奈學姐和長門挑選了以後  毫不客氣地衝進了試衣間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可相當花時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.51,0:08:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期間頻遭女性顧客冷眼  我們等了大約一小時  三個人終於都換好出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  都非常合適哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦  是我給挑選的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是實玖瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是我挑的  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會看走眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實  這是在春日強行加上的服裝中最頂級的貨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  超合適  這個給YES
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:59.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（YESだね：捏自Brain Power(機動神腦)的台詞）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是這個國家的古典民俗衣著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然胸口有點難受  不過好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就準備好了  那麼出發吧  去盆舞會場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過盆舞啊  感覺好像很久沒有看到過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  實玖瑠  你想要玩的撈金魚也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撈個痛快吧  黑色凸眼金魚可是加200分的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去玩吧  來比比看能撈多少條如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我PASS  比起那個我還是對食物有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長門你覺得如何  要吃點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對那種東西有興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  800日元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13條  雖然是大豐收但我不需要那麼多  就只要了一條
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是完全撈不起來  撈金魚好難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  正常人是撈不了那麼多的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有訣竅的話就很簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  有希  那個面具是怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎…不過為什麼要這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是波長相合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因為是宇宙人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  不管了  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一塊還沒轉過  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只吃一個的話沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  盆舞也差不多跳完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來玩煙火吧  煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙火…嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得穿這身  今天就一起做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對  對面的店裡就有賣的  就去河邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很開心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柿崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（此處捏自「超時空要塞Macross」劇場版的柿崎機(VF-1A)）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盆舞  煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼明天是捉昆蟲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日啊  雖說玩也沒問題  你暑假作業做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說一點也沒有動的我說這話有點那啥就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了  那種程度的作業有三天不就全部做完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我七月就解決掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種麻煩事就得事先趕緊收拾了  再毫無後顧之憂地玩到爽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是正確的享受暑假的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這種傢伙腦子這麼好  上天對於人的參數調整還真是隨便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之  明天去捉昆蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉到的蟲子最多的那個人…  這樣吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把團長的權力讓給他一天！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣呢  只要是蟲子的話什麼都可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:12:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…只能抓蟬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  這就是SOS團內部的捉蟬大戰  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只多抓了一隻也算贏！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了祈雨  我把晴天娃娃用五寸釘刺著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到來的卻是萬里無雲的好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟬也為今年夏天最熱的一天而雀躍不已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  蟬能夠拿來吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許弄成天婦羅會是極品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我有時會想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天婦羅會不會只是外面一層麵衣好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  那蟬也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快道歉！快向全國的天婦羅店道歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓青春年華的高中生拿著蟲網與籠子聚集在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什麼企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊  沒有蟲網的話怎麼抓蟬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是問那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們開始了  優勝者可以當一天的團長！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒在聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的想贏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  捕蟬的話  小學不都試過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊  盡力而行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已經抓到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是蟬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海…海格力斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:37.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（大力神獨角仙(D.hercules)，胸部有大而光滑的角）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公佈結果！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.03,0:15:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠一隻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希四隻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古泉七隻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛九隻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.11,0:15:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後最高紀錄是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  你不用說都知道是誰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我！十二隻！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  團長之座一天都讓不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家真是可惜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會真的想把它們做成天婦羅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  你想吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼成我要吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開個玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底  還是要有放生的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放它們一條生路  以後說不定會來報恩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快回山裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再被抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是說得好聽  但你這只是單方面的捕捉後放生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是接著的下一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日不知從何處找來了兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還難得為我們爭取了機會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本地超市的紀念促銷宣傳活動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你們加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作內容是吸引顧客
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…連我都非得裝成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是暑假的兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有別的做法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且春日只是在一旁涼快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下來與她的日薪要是一樣的話  絕對要暴動的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於能明白脫皮後蛇的心情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  真是一個好例子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長大叔也謝謝大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要大叔的感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個囉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個外套就是工錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很早之前就很想要的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔也看在實玖瑠的份上說送給我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隻青蛙要放在社團室裡當作紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實玖瑠  你想什麼時候穿都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我許可的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳池  盂蘭盆節  捕蟲  兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後春日進行的就是天體觀測
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  這就是這個年代的望遠鏡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與開普勒時代的沒什麼不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我覺得相差很遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是買來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我小時候的興趣就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看見木星衛星的時候真的十分激動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:17:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是火星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.27,0:18:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不希望它存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章魚一樣的怪物蜿蜒地計劃著征服地球的圖像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要說好話我也不覺得有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是十分友好的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在地下的大空洞偷偷地生活著的害羞人種
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓地球人感到吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你腦內的火星人到底有多麼文雅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來找UFO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在衛星軌道上  一定有異星人的先遣隊在待機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  實玖瑠也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…呃…UFO  UFO…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假還未結束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日接著要做的是——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到擊球中心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要到那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早看見甲子園的新聞我就想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能只滿足於那些雜牌的棒球比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們SOS團要建成以全國為目標的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能量到底是從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是細胞內的線粒體與常人不一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些能量能為世人用上一點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後  誰也不能阻止春日定下的定額消耗態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不停地跟著行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也去了真正的煙火大會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也將砰砰地射上高空\N又碰碰地綻放的煙火觀賞到滿足為止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在另一天  我們則在縣邊境的河邊參加釣蝦虎魚大會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  實玖瑠  竿子竿子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧  我會拿回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下還有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是固定節目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但應該沒有人真會去玩的試膽大會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看了只有宣傳非常像那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但內容大家都心知肚明的大製作電影的聯播
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在完全是淡季的會漂來水母的海灘上進行海水浴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到所有人都達到全清才能離開的保齡球懲罰遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:21:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑戰喉嚨極限的長時間耐久卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至覺得包括了很多與夏天無關的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  我們在這兩週內玩到再起不能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是8月30日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課題都完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀唉呀  總算順利完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…這樣就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…嗯  也就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還有什麼想做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想好好睡一覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.83,0:21:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好  這個夏天都幹了不少事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四處遊玩  也穿上了浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟬也抓了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:22:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到這裡為止吧  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這傢伙還有什麼遺憾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今天就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.25,0:22:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就空下來當是預備日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好好地休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.01,0:22:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後天再在社團教室見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.50,0:22:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊  作業完全沒有做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.31,0:22:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8月31日  暑假的最後一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.18,0:22:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正怎麼努力都不可能把作業做完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:22:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒法消除玩後的疲勞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.94,0:22:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就這樣子拖拖拉拉地過了懶散的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:01.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.79,0:23:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.29,0:23:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管了  由它去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.93,0:23:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧  明天還要上學
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.32,0:23:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關燈睡覺
